This rails application was deployed to AWS with a single command.  What happens when it runs?  
<br/>
<ol>
<li>A shell script passes a CloudFormation template containing the instance and security group definitions to Boto.</li>
<li>Boto kicks off the stack creation on AWS.</li>
<li>A CloudInit script in the instance definition bootstraps puppet and git, then downloads repos from Github.</li>  
<li>Puppet provisions rvm, ruby, and rails.</li> 
<li>Finally, CloudInit runs Webrick as a daemon.</li>   
</ol>
<br/>To do: 
<br/>
