<li>Let Puppet Master and Capistrano handle instance and app provisioning, respectively.</li>
<li>Get better feedback on errors that may occur during this process.</li>
<li>Introduce an Elastic Load Balancer and set autoscale to 2.</li>
<li>Get a VPN tunnel to campus and access ND data</li>
<li>Work toward automatic app redeployments triggered by git pushes.</li>
</ol> 
